StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.INSERTSENIORLECTURER(pFirstName IN VARCHAR2, pSurname IN VARCHAR2,&lt;br/&gt;pTitle IN VARCHAR2, pAddress IN VARCHAR2, pPhone IN NUMBER, pPostcode IN NUMBER,&lt;br/&gt;pCampusLocation IN VARCHAR2, pIdBuilding IN NUMBER, pNumberOffice IN VARCHAR2, pStaffType IN VARCHAR2,&lt;br/&gt; pArea IN VARCHAR2, pLecturerType IN VARCHAR2, pNumberPhd IN NUMBER, &lt;br/&gt;pNumberMaster IN NUMBER, pNumberHonours IN NUMBER) AS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; INSERT INTO SeniorLecturer_table &lt;br/&gt; VALUES(SeniorLecturer_obj(sequenceSeniorLecturerID.Nextval, pSurname, pFirstName, pTitle, pAddress, pPhone, pPostcode, &lt;br/&gt; pCampusLocation, pIdBuilding, pNumberOffice, pStaffType, pArea, pLecturerType, pNumberPhd, pNumberMaster, pNumberHonours));&lt;br/&gt; COMMIT;&lt;br/&gt;END insertSeniorLecturer;
